    <s:String x:Key="str_About_Description" xmlns:s="clr-namespace:System;assembly=mscorlib">Developed as an academic project for the OPAM discipline. The system allows storing and managing a product catalog: add, edit and delete items, search and filter by category, and export data to a CSV file.</s:String>
